bits.name: ephSource
bits.description: 0 = not available, 1 = GNSS transmission, 2 = external aiding, 3-7 = other

bits.description: 0 = not available, 1 = GNSS transmission, 2 = external aiding, 3-7 = other

bits.name: anoAopUsability

values.30: The usability period is more than 30 days

values.0: Almanac can no longer be used

sub_fields.name: anoAopUsability
sub_fields.description: How long the receiver will be able to use the orbit data from now on:

values.30: The usability period is more than 30 days
values.range_30_to_1: The usability period is between n-1 and n days
values.0: Data can no longer be used

bits.description: How long the receiver will be able to use the stored ephemeris data from now on: 31 = The usability period is unknown, 30 = The usability period is more than 450 minutes, 30 > n > 0 = The usability period is between (n-1)*15 and n*15 minutes, 0 = Ephemeris can no longer be used

bits.name: ephSource
bits.description: 0 = not available, 1 = GNSS transmission, 2 = external aiding, 3-7 = other

bits.name: almUsability
bits.description: How long the receiver will be able to use the stored almanac data from now on: 31 = The usability period is unknown, 30 = The usability period is more than 30 days, 30 > n > 0 = The usability period is between n-1 and n days, 0 = Almanac can no longer be used

bits.name: almSource
bits.description: 0 = not available, 1 = GNSS transmission, 2 = external aiding, 3-7 = other

bits.name: anoAopUsability
bits.description: How long the receiver will be able to use the orbit data from now on: 31 = The usability period is unknown, 30 = The usability period is more than 30 days, 30 > n > 0 = The usability period is between n-1 and n days, 0 = Data can no longer be used

bits.name: type
bits.description: Type of orbit data: 0 = No orbit data available, 1 = AssistNow Offline data, 2 = AssistNow Autonomous data, 3-7 = Other orbit data
